1. Enable Caching

•	Response Caching: Cache frequent, read-only responses at the gateway to reduce backend load and latency.
•	Azure API Management: Use the <cache-lookup> and <cache-store> policies.
•	AWS API Gateway: Enable API Gateway caching for methods.
Example (Azure APIM Policy):

